tasks.title: Class generators
tasks.description: The todos are going to be objects that will be dynamically created.

tasks.title: Task properties
tasks.description: At a minimum tasks should have a title, description, dueDate and priority

tasks.title: Projects
tasks.description: The todo list should have projects or separate lists of todos. When a user first opens the app, there should be some sort of ‘default’ project to which all of their todos are put. Users should be able to create new projects and choose which project their todos go into.

tasks.title: Webpack
tasks.description: Go back to webpack tutorial to implement it in this project

tasks.title: Local Storage
tasks.description: Set up a function that saves the projects (and todos) to localStorage every time a new project (or todo) is created, and another function that looks for that data in localStorage when your app is first loaded.

tasks.title: Keep Calm
tasks.description: Keep calm and learn front-end development
